title: Damian Marley- Mr. Marley
description:
Mr. Marley 
Damian Marley a.k.a. Jr. Gong brought to life his musical heritage with "Mr. Marley", skillfully produced by brother Stephen as one of the first projects conceived by Ghetto Youths International. Amongst the outstanding tracks on this album are "Love And Inity", a vital, rhythmic song, the hard core "Old War Chant", the pulsating "Mr. Marley", and the musical introduction "Me Name Jr. Gong". 

Tracklist
1) Trouble 
2) Love and Inity 
3) 10,000 Chariots 
4) Old War Chant 
5) Party Time
6) Kingston 12
7) Keep On Growing
8) Searching (So Much Bubble) 
9) One More Cup of Coffee
10) Julie

12) Mr. Marley
